    <h2 class="post-title"><a href="http://duckofminerva.com/2018/03/pinkers-enlightenment-and-liberal-world-order.html" rel="bookmark" title="Pinker’s Enlightenment and Liberal World Order">Pinker’s Enlightenment and Liberal World Order</a></h2>
    
    <div class="post-meta">
	
		<span class="post-date"><a href="http://duckofminerva.com/2018/03/pinkers-enlightenment-and-liberal-world-order.html" title="Pinker’s Enlightenment and Liberal World Order">2018-03-12</a></span>
		
