    <h2 class="post-title"><a href="http://duckofminerva.com/2018/03/remembering-lee-ann-fujii-a-friend-and-a-fighter.html" rel="bookmark" title="Remembering Lee Ann Fujii, a Friend and a Fighter">Remembering Lee Ann Fujii, a Friend and a Fighter</a></h2>
    
    <div class="post-meta">
	
		<span class="post-date"><a href="http://duckofminerva.com/2018/03/remembering-lee-ann-fujii-a-friend-and-a-fighter.html" title="Remembering Lee Ann Fujii, a Friend and a Fighter">2018-03-10</a></span>
		
		<span class="date-sep"> / </span>
			
		<span class="post-author"><a href="http://duckofminerva.com/author/jbusby" title="Posts by Josh Busby" rel="author">Josh Busby</a></span>
		
		<span class="date-sep"> / </span>
		
		<a href="http://duckofminerva.com/2018/03/remembering-lee-ann-fujii-a-friend-and-a-fighter.html#comments"><span class="dsq-postid" data-dsqidentifier="31865 http://duckofminerva.com/?p=31865">3 Comments</span></a>		
				
										
