    <div class="post-meta">
	
		<span class="post-date"><a href="http://duckofminerva.com/2018/03/international-womens-day-political-crisis-as-windows-of-opportunity.html" title="International Women&#8217;s Day: political crisis as windows of opportunity">2018-03-06</a></span>
		
