		<a href="http://duckofminerva.com/2018/03/international-womens-day-political-crisis-as-windows-of-opportunity.html#respond"><span class="dsq-postid" data-dsqidentifier="31839 http://duckofminerva.com/?p=31839"><span class="comment">0 Comments</span></span></a>		
				
										
