    <h2 class="post-title"><a href="http://duckofminerva.com/2018/02/broken-ir-it-is-worse-than-walt-lets-on.html" rel="bookmark" title="Broken IR? It is worse than Walt lets on">Broken IR? It is worse than Walt lets on</a></h2>
    
    <div class="post-meta">
	
		<span class="post-date"><a href="http://duckofminerva.com/2018/02/broken-ir-it-is-worse-than-walt-lets-on.html" title="Broken IR? It is worse than Walt lets on">2018-02-22</a></span>
		
		<span class="date-sep"> / </span>
			
