    <div class="post-meta">
	
		<span class="post-date"><a href="http://duckofminerva.com/2018/02/trauma-in-common-us-gun-violence-and-violence-in-armed-conflict.html" title="Trauma in Common: US Gun Violence and Violence in Armed Conflict">2018-02-21</a></span>
		
		<span class="date-sep"> / </span>
			
